high_descs: move to the bin to the left of the sink
pick up soap from the bin
clean the soap in the sink
move to the right side of the sink
put the soap in a cabinet
anns.task_desc: Put wet soap in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the red garbage bin on the floor by the toilet.
Pick up the bar of soap from the garbage bin.
Put the bar of soap in the near by sink, rinse it off, and take it out of the sink.
Move slightly backwards away from the sink
Put the bar of soap in the cabinet which is below and to the left of the sink on the right, then close the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned bar of soap in a cabinet.

high_descs: Move to the opposite side of the room facing the red trash bin on the floor to the right of the toilet
Pick up the soap inside of the trash bin
Move to the right facing the bathroom sink on the left side, wash the soap
Move back to the cupboard under the sink
Place the soap inside of the cupboard under the sink
anns.task_desc: Move a clean bar of soap to the bathroom cupboard
